<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=9552&amp;p=103803#p103803"><![CDATA[
Two things might help:<br /><ul><li>Does CV3 normally put anything in $6000-$7FFF? If not, something that'd normally be in one of the switchable banks could be relocated to PRG RAM there. </li><li>Does CV3 use the DMC? If so, the music can be rewritten not to use it, freeing up $C000-$DFFF. </li></ul><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=9">tepples</a> — Sat Dec 01, 2012 12:15 pm</p><hr />
